# Build context for stream-client/Dockerfile is this directory. Exclude things
# that aren't needed in the image or that trip BuildKit.

# Self-referential symlink inside factorio-client/ (factorio-client/factorio-client
# -> ./factorio-client) breaks BuildKit's checksum walker. Ignore it.
factorio-client/factorio-client

# Huge / unused subtrees of Factorio installs.
factorio-client/doc-html
factorio-client/saves

# Agent source isn't needed for the stream-client image.
agent/

# Repo noise.
README.md
*.md
.git
